{"tid":2327327,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"社工總工會總幹事許麗明被控阻差辦公 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-12-16T03:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T05:14:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0010a3a996f5f7bef297c35d02d18721f7fe5542","tid":2327327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"社工兼社總總幹事許麗明於去年9.29「全球反極權大遊行」警民衝突期間被捕，一度遭控以襲警罪，惟控方於案件開審前改控以阻差辦公罪。涉案警員供稱，當日看到被告情緒激動衝向警方及被捕人士，又大叫「你哋唔好打啲小朋友」。他要求被告離開不果，反遭被告推胸及撥小腹致兩度跌倒。裁判官鍾明新今宣讀裁決，裁定許罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前於結案陳詞曾指，涉案的警員19035莊的朗證供不可信亦不可靠，指莊原本供稱起初看到被告時，被告身處救護車後方，證供與現場影片不符，莊看片後稱記錯。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，控方不能在毫無合理疑點下證明被告有意圖阻差辦公，而被告身處現場的身份是社工。控方亦無法證明被告的行為對莊造成實際阻礙，令他難以執行職務。莊也從沒指出被告行為如何對他的工作造成阻撓、或導致他難以執行職務，亦沒任何客觀環境證據證明其職務受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/KGNJZNU5B5DT7GSH4MDQPBET3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FKGNJZNU5B5DT7GSH4MDQPBET3Y%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUwz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=4e51cea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FKGNJZNU5B5DT7GSH4MDQPBET3Y%2F&h=3991c046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/KGNJZNU5B5DT7GSH4MDQPBET3Y/</a>"},{"pid":"2d576b33be17280c19009bfd3dbd16d5e6c2a294","tid":2327327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a19412f0d8388ee43e58dfb9fe8e739efbb10c","tid":2327327,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>裁判官鍾明新今宣讀裁決，裁定許罪名不成立，直指警員證供不可靠。<br />\n<br />\n涉案警員早前出庭作供，稱當日看到被告情緒激動衝向警方及被捕人士，並大叫「你哋唔好打啲小朋友」。他要求被告離開不果，反遭被告推胸口致跌倒。警員又謂處理示威活動時若看見社工，不會拘捕他們，但他當時不知被告是社工。辯方指被告當日正正身穿「我哋係社工，守護公義」上衣，警員只謂沒留意。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官今指涉案警員證供供與現場片段內容有出入，認為許於案發時態度合作，跟隨警員指示離開，無意對抗警員，她亦無時間或機會阻撓警員。裁判官指警員證供不可靠。</strong>"},{"pid":"1409c1b95c396405003b35441f423dd177a0e55d","tid":2327327,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7134d6790de6494136da87b09932aec96cd58d7a","tid":2327327,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59036934321b8ecf06cc9f913a64ce90e0dc3cf9","tid":2327327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7134d6790de6494136da87b09932aec96cd58d7a","tid":2327327,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f8d687478388f7053bb5ba74e6a5b554ebd8e6","tid":2327327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1409c1b95c396405003b354